AREA CONCEPT - OSPF


R1
en
config t 
host R1
int eth0/0
ip add 12.1.1.1 255.255.255.0
no shutdown
!
int loop1
ip add 1.1.1.1 255.255.255.0
no shutdown
!
router ospf 100
network 12.1.1.0 0.0.0.255 area 1
network 1.1.1.0 0.0.0.255 area 1
do wr

